title: It really is that easy! Res Lease in Austin. 3 Beds, 3 Baths
posting_body: ['Built in 2021 Clawson Place Townhomes offers several two story luxury townhomes!', 'The kitchen opens to a living area with large windows to give natural light to the space, all stainless steel appliances, refrigerator included, and spacious laundry room with washer and dryer hookups.', "Each bedroom with it's own connected bathroom, downstairs bedroom featuring built in cabinets and drawers, perfect for a guest room or office space.", 'Upstairs bedrooms with ensuite bathrooms and walk in closets.', 'Clawson Place Townhomes includes assigned parking, a dog run with a doggy station being installed, and soon to come electric car charging station.', 'Located off Ben White and minutes from the South Congress area, local dining and shopping are within walking/biking distance!', "These townhomes are sure to impress, don't miss your change to call this one home!", 'Apply TODAY!', ' ***', 'Text Message FEDERICO', 'to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 3908260)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Matt Leschber, 1836 Realty & Property Mgmt']
